Package: redlist
Type: Package
Title: Access and Analyze IUCN Red List Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Stanislas Mahussi", 
           family = "Gandaho", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           email = "gandahostanmah@gmail.com", 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-4969-1252")))
Maintainer: Stanislas Mahussi Gandaho <gandahostanmah@gmail.com>
Description: Provides tools to access and analyze data from the IUCN Red List API.
    This package includes functions to retrieve species assessments, conservation statuses, 
    and population trends, as well as taxonomic and distribution information for species 
    listed on the IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. The package is designed to support 
    conservation efforts and biodiversity research by enabling users to programmatically 
    access up-to-date Red List data.
